Inc. and the International Society for Diseases of the Esophagus.

DOI: 10.1111/j.1442-2050.2011.01188.x
PMID: 21418125 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


260. Trop Med Int Health. 2011 Jun;16(6):731-6. doi: 
